name: provstore-api
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "provstore-api" %}
{% set version = "0.1.3" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/provstore-api-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c43289a1774a7ad1dfc9a1c5dcae45fa39ca563fff2e1d895774dd81de956466

build:
  number: 5
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - prov >=1.0.0
    - python
    - requests

test:
  imports:
    - provstore
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/millar/provstore-api
  summary: ProvStore API client
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - vinisalazar
